<br>
I make a great melee assistant, and if need be, can even pull and stand toe to toe with critters... Add in Crit Strike, Envenom, and fast weapons with high Dex and Qui? I hit a LOT in combat! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
When looking to fill out a group, don't forget us shades! We'll be yer friends! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#110d03><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/ukelleighm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KelleighM</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hibernian Defender Trainee</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#006400>(4/26/02 4:51:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Nightshades are NOT useless in groups!</span><hr size=1> Having a nightshade in the group is a wonderful thing.  The problem is that the nightshade class seems to be 'the flavor of the month'.  There's ALOT of you out there right now.  <br>
<br>
I've also run into a fair number of 'shades whose primary goal is to level enough to RvR as quickly as possible.  Unfortunately, they don't seem to give two hoots about any FUN the rest of the group is entitled to.<br>
<br>
Shades who want into a group that already have a shade and a ranger (another 'flavor of the month' member), will just have to be patient with people who don't want to have another.  Keep looking, stay upbeat and polite, or start your own group.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#110d03><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/ufrostryder.showPublicProfile?language=EN>frostryder</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hibernian Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#006400>(5/1/02 9:30:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.frostryder.net/files/mailpix/Nighshade.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Nightshades are NOT useless in groups!</span><hr size=1> Aye, that's true... I do want to level as fast as possible, as does everyone, but the fun of the group is the most important thing to me <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
That part that's hard to understand as it's happening, is that people don't tell you they don't have room or already have a shade or two, they just don't say anything... So, there you stand like the last kid picked for any sport in school <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
On a positive note, I made 32 finally, got Climb Walls, and am still having fun! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#110d03><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/ukelleighm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KelleighM</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hibernian Defender Trainee</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#006400>(5/1/02 4:58:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Nightshades are NOT useless in groups!</span><hr size=1> Not *everyone* wants to level as fast as possible.  For myself, having fun is the most important reason I play this game.  Social interaction is a very close second.  Fortunately, a good number of people that I hang out with in Hibernia feel the same way.<br>
<br>
Xp is great when it happens, but if I'm not having fun, I couldn't be bothered.<br>
<br>
I suspect that you're on the other end of the spectrum of my grouping experience lately.  After the 10th nightshade pages me and asks to join my group, I am really sick and tired of explaining that I already have one.  And honestly, I gave up the list thing when I left EQ.<br>
<br>
Congrats on 32! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=5.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.showNextMessage?topicID=5.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=5.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.threadControl?topicID=5.topic><img src=3- http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub49.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="hiberniaonguiniverefrm1">General<option value="hiberniaonguiniverefrm8">Roleplay - Tales of the Realm<option value="hiberniaonguiniverefrm18">FAQ & Archive<option value="hiberniaonguiniverefrm7">For Sale/Trade or Craft Requests<option value